hadiths[220]{hadithnumber,text}:
1599,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney gharon mein bhi namaz (nafl) padha karo. unhein qabristaan na bana lo."
1600,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney masjid mein khajoor ki chataai ko khada kar key hujra sa bana liya (taake sukoon sey raat ki namaz padh saken) Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kaee raaten is mein namaz padhi yahan tak ke log bhi aap key qarib jama honey lag gaey (aur aap ki namaz key sath namaz padhney lagey) phir eik raat unhoney aap ki aawaz mehsus na ki. unhoney samjha ke aap soey huye hain. un mein sey kuchh khakaarney lagey taake aap (jaag kar) un ki taraf tashrif ley aayen. (magar aap na nikley, phir subah key waqt) aap ney farmaya : jo kuchh tum kartey rahey ho main dekhta raha hun (magar is liye nahin nikla ke) mujhey khatra paida huwa ke kahin (tumharey zauq shoq ki wajeh sey) tum par raat ki namaz farz hi na kar di jaey. aur agar tum par farz kar di jati to tum isey ada na kar paatey, lihaza aey logo raat ki namaz apney gharon mein padh liya karo kyonkey farz namaz key ilawa insan ki afzal namaz wo hai jo ghar mein padhey."
1601,Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (eik dafa) Maghrib ki namaz banu Abdul-Ash'hal ki masjid mein padhi. jab aap namaz (farz) sey farigh huye to kuchh log uth kar nawaafil (maghrib ki sunnatein) padhney lagey. aap ney farmaya : ye namaz gharon mein padha karo.
1602,"Hazrat Saad bin Hisham sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey mila aur un sey namaz witr key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : kya main tujhey us shakhsiyat key barey mein na bataun jo ruey-zameen par basney waley insanon mein sey sab sey ziyada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz witr ko janti ho? Saad ney kaha : han, zarur. unhoney farmaya : wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) hain. unsey ja kar puchho, phir wapis aa kar mujhey bhi batao ke unhoney kya jawab diya, chunanche main Hazrat Hakim bin Aflah key paas aaya aur unhein bhi sath chalney key liye kaha. wo kehney lagey : main to unkey paas nahin jaunga kyonkey mainey un sey guzarish ki thi ke aap un do ladney waley girohon (Usmani o Alvi) key barey mein kuch bhi na kahin magar unhoney meri baat nahin maana balke apni marzi ki. mainey unhein qism di (ke wo zarur chalen) to wo merey sath chal padey aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas pahunchey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney un sey kaha : ye tumharey sath kon hai? mainey kaha : Saad bin Hisham. unhoney farmaya : kon sa Hisham ? mainey kaha : Hisham bin Aamir. to aap ney unkey liye rehmat ki dua ki aur farmaya : Aamir bahut achey insan they. merey sathi ney kaha : aey ummul-Mominin ! aap mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key akhlaqe-aaliya key barey mein bataiye. to farmaney lagin : kya tum Quran nahin padhtey? mainey kaha : kyon nahin (padhta hun) unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key akhlaqe-aaliya aen Quran key mutabiq they. mainey uthney ka irada kya to merey zehen mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qiyamullail (raat ki ibadat ) ka khayal aaya. mainey kaha : aey ummul-Mominin ! mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qiyamullail key barey mein bataiye. unhoney farmaya : kya tum ye sura ( یایھا المزمل ) nahin padhtey ? mainey kaha : kyon nahin ( padhta hun. ) farmaney lagin : Allah Taala ney is sura key shuru mein raat ka qiyam farz kya tha. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sahaba eik saal tak qiyam kartey rahey yahan tak ke unkey paon sooj gaey. Allah Taala ney is sura ki aakhiri aayaten (doosra rukoo) baara mahiney rok rakhen, phir un aayaat mein takhfeef nazil farmaai to qiyamullail nafl ban gaya jabkey pehley farz tha. mainey, phir uthney ka irada kya ke achcha merey zehen mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz witr ka khayal aa gaya. mainey kaha : aey ummul-Mominin! mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz witr key barey mein bataiye. unhoney farmaya : hum raat ko aap ki miswak aur tahaarat ka pani tayyar karkey rakh detey they, phir Allah Taala jab pasand farmata aap ko jaga deta. aap (uth kar) miswak farmatey aur wuzu kartey, phir aath rakaat is tarah padhtey ke un mein sey kisi rakat key baad nahin bethtey they magar aathwein rakat key baad bethtey, Allah Taala ka zikr farmatey aur duayen kartey, phir itni aawaz sey salam kehtey ke hamen sunai deta, phir salam key baad bethey-bethey do rakat padhtey, phir eik rakat padhtey beta! is tarah ye giyara rakatein ban gaeen, phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki umr ziyada ho gaee aur bojhal ho gaey to saat rakaat padhtey aur salam key baad bethey-bethey do rakatein padhtey. beta ! is tarah ye no rakatein ban gaeen. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab koi namaz shuru farma letey to munasib samajhtey they ke usey hamesha padha karen aur agar kabhi neend ya bimari ya koi takleef raat ki namaz sey rukawat ban jati to din ko (bajaey giyara key) baara rakaat padh letey. aur mujhey ilm nahin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kabhi eik raat mein pura Quran padha ho ya kabhi subh tak sari raat namaz padhtey rahey hon ya Ramzanul-Mubarak key ilawa kabhi pura mahina rozey rakhey hon, phir main Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key paas aaya aur unkey samney ye puri hadees bayan ki. aap farmaney lagey : sach kaha Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney wallah! agar main unkey paas jata hota to zarur jata ke wo mujhey baraahe-raast ye hadees bayan farmaatin. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees meri kitab mein aisey hi hai. main nahin janta aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key witr key bayan mein kis sey ghalati ho qaee?"
1603,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman ki bina par sawab ki niyat sey Ramzanul-Mubarak ki raaton mein qiyam karey (namaze-taravih padhey ) to uskey pehley sab gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
1604,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney eman key taqaazey sey aur sirf sawab hasil karney key liye Ramzanul-Mubarak ki raaton ka qiyam kya, uskey pehley sab gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
1605,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik raat masjid mein namaz ( taravih ) kuch log bhi aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz padhney lagey, phir agli raat aap ney ( masjid mein) namaz padhi to log pehley sey ziyada ho gaey, phir teesri ya chauthi raat to sab log hi jama ho gaey lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif na laye. jab subh hui to aap ney farmaya : raat jo tum ney kya main dekh raha tha (yani tumhara ijtima aur zauq o shoq ) magar mujhey aaney sey ye chiz rok rahi thi ke mujhey khatra paida huwa ke kahin ye namaz tum par farz hi na kar di jaey. aur ye Ramzanul-Mubarak ki baat hai."
1606,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hamney Ramzanul-Mubarak mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath rozey rakhey. aap ney hamen raat ki namaz nahin padhaai yahan tak ke is maah mubarak key saat din baqi reh gaey. aap ney hamen raat ki namaz ( taravih ) padhaai yahan tak ke raat ka tihai hissa guzar gaya, phir agley din hamen namaz nahin padhaai, phir pachchiswin raat hamen namaz padhaai yahan tak ke nisf raat guzar gaee. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hi khub hota agar aap baqi raat bhi namaz padhatey. aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Imam key sath uskey farigh honey tak namaz padhi, uskey liye puri raat key qiyam ka sawab likha jata hai (chahey uskey baad wo so hi jaey). phir aap ney agli raat namaz nahin padhaai yahan tak ke us maah mubarak key teen din baqi reh gaey to aap ney hamen sattaiswin raat namaz padhaai aur apney ghar walon aur biwiyon ko bhi jama farmaya (aur itni lambi namaz padhaai ) yahan tak ke hamen khatra huwa ke hum sey falah reh jaeygi. ( Juber kehtey hain ) mainey (Hazrat Abu-Zar sey) puchha : « falah » sey kya murad hai? unhoney farmaya : sehri."
1607,"Hazrat Naeem bin Ziyad sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma ko teiswin ( shehar ) key member par farmatey suna ke hamney Ramzanul-Mubarak ki teiswin raat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tihai raat tak qiyam kya, phir pachiswin raat mein aap key sath nisf raat tak qiyam kya, phir sattaiswin raat aap key sath itni der tak qiyam kya ke hamney samjha : hum « falah » ( sehri ) nahin kha sakengey."
1608,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs sota hai to shetan uskey sar par teen girhein laga deta hai. aur har gireh detey waqt ye padhta hai : lambi raat hai, so ja, phir agar wo jaag kar Allah ka zikr karey to eik gireh khul jati hai agar wo wuzu karey to dusri gireh bhi khul jati hai aur agar wo namaz shuru kar dey to teesri gireh bhi khul jati hai aur wo khush dil aur chust o chalak ho jata hai warna bad dil aur sust rehta hai."
1609,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik aadmi ka zikr kya gaya jo sari raat sota raha yahan tak ke subh ho gaee. aap ney farmaya is shakhs key kanon mein shetan ney peshab kar diya tha.
1610,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! falan shakhs raat namaz sey soya raha yahan tak ke roshni ho gaee. aap ney farmaya : uskey kanon mein shetan ney peshab kar diya tha."
1611,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala us aadmi par reham farmaai jo raat ko utha aur us ney namaz ( tahajjud ) padhi, phir us ney apni biwi ko jagaya, us ney bhi namaz (tahajjud) padhi aur agar wo (uthney sey) inkar karey to uskey chehrey par pani key chheentey maarey. isi tarah Allah Taala reham farmaai us aurat par jo raat ko uthi aur namaz padhi, phir apney khawind ko jagaya aur us ney bhi namaz padhi aur agar us ney inkar kya to uskey chehrey par pani key chheentey maarey."
1612,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik dafa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat key waqt unkey aur sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) key paas aaye aur farmaya : tum raat ki namaz nahin padhtey ? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamari roohen Allah Taala key haath mein hain. jab Allah Taala chahega hamen jagaa dega. jab mainey ye baat kahi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wapis tashrif ley gaey. mainey suna, aap apni raan mubarak par (afsos aur narazi sey) haath maartay ja rahey they : (و کان الانسان اکثر شییء جدلا) insan sab sey badh kar kat hujjat hai."
1613,"Hazrat Ali ibn abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat key waqt merey aur Fatima Raziallahu anhuma key paas tashrif laye aur hamen namaz ( tahajjud ) key liye jagaya, phir apney ghar tashrif ley gaey aur kafi der tak namaz padhtey rahey. aap ney hamari taraf sey koi aawaz ya aahat na suni to dobara tashrif laye aur hamen phir jagaya aur farmaya : utho aur namaz padho. main aankhen milta huwa utha aur keh raha tha : Allah ki qism ! hum to wohi namaz padhengey jo Allah ney hamari qismat mein likhi hai. hamari roohen Allah Taala key haath mein hain agar wo chahega to hamen utha dega. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni raan mubarak par haath maartay wapis tashrif ley gaey aur farma rahey they : hum wohi namaz padhengey jo Allah ney hamari qismat mein likhi hai aur haqiqat ye hai ke insan sab sey ziyada kat hujjat hai."
1614,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ramzanul-Mubarak key baad afzal rozey Allah Taala key mahiney Mohrim key hain aur farz namazon key baad afzal namaz raat ki namaz ( tahajjud ) hai."
1615,"Hazrat Humed bin Abdur-Rehman sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : farz namaz key baad afzal namaz raat ki namaz ( tahajjud ) hai aur Ramzanul-Mubarak key baad afzal rozey Mohrim key hain. Shoba bin Hujjaaj ney us riwayat ko mursal bayan kya hai."
1616,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen (qism key) aadmi wo hain jin sey Allah Taala ko mohabbat hai : eik wo aadmi jo kisi qom key paas aaya aur unsey Allah Taala key naam par sawal kya. apni kisi rishtedari ki bina par sawal nahin kya lekin kisi ney usey kuch na diya magar eik aadmi un sab logon ko peechey chhod kar aagey chala gaya aur us (saail) ko poshida taur par maal diya. uskey us atiye ka kisi ko ilm na huwa, siwaye Allah Taala key aur us shakhs key jis ko us ney diya. aur eik wo shakhs ke kuch log sari raat chaltey rahey yahan tak ke jab neend unko har chiz sey ziyada piyari lagney lagi to wo utrey aur so gaey magar wo shakhs khada ho kar merey samney gidgidaney laga aur (namaz mein) meri aayaat padhney laga aur eik wo shakhs jo eik lashkar mein shamil tha. us lashkar ka dushman sey muqabla huwa. sab shikast kha gaey magar wo Sina taan kar aagey badha yahan tak ke wo maara gaya ya usey fatah mil gaee."
1617,Hazrat Masruq sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko kon-sa amal ziyada pasand tha? unhoney farmaya : jo hamesha kya jaey (chahey kam hi ho) mainey kaha : aap raat ko kis waqt tahajjud key liye uthtey they? unhoney farmaya : jab murgh ki ( pehli ) aawaz suntey.
1618,"Hazrat Aasim bin Humed bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kin alfaz sey qiyamullail ki shuruat kya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : tum ney mujh sey wo chiz puchhi hai jo tum sey pehley kisi ney nahin puchhi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) das dafa « Allahu-akbar », das dafa « Alhamdulillah », das dafa « subhan Allah », das dafa (la Ilaah illa Allah) aur das dafa « استغفراللہ » kehtey they, phir farmatey : aey Allah ! mujhey maaf farma, mujhey hidayat dey, mujhey rizq ata farma aur mujhey aafiyat o sehat dey. aur main qiyamat key din Allah Taala key samney khada honey ki tangi sey Allah Taala ki panah chahta hun."
1619,"Hazrat Rabeea bin Kaab Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key hujrey key qarib sota tha. jab aap raat ko (tahajjud key liye) uthtey to main sunta ke aap der tak (subhan Allah rabbul-Alameen ) pak hai Allah jo jahano ka rab hai, padhtey rehtey phir der tak (subhanallahi w bi hamdihi) Allah Taala tamam uyub o naqaayis sey pak hai aur tamam taarifon wala hai. padhtey"
1620,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko tahajjud key liye uthtey to ye dua padhtey : ( اللھم لک الحمد . ۔ . wala قوۃ illa billah) aey Allah! terey hi liye sab tareef hai. to aasmano aur zaminon ka Noor hai. aur un logon ka Noor hai jo un mein hain, aur terey hi liye sab tareef hai. to aasmano o zamin aur unkey darmyan tamam logon ko qaaim rakhney wala hai. aur terey hi liye sab tareef hai. to aasmano, zaminon aur un mein rehney walon ka badshah hai aur terey hi liye sab tareef hai. to bar-haq hai. terey wadey bar-haq hain. jannat haq hai aur jahannam haq hai, aur qiyamat haq hai, aur tamam Nabi haq hain aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi haq hain. main tera hi mutee o farman-bardar huwa aur tujhi par mainey bharosa kya aur tujhi par main eman laya aur teri hi madad sey main (kuffar sey) jhagadta hun aur terey huzur hi faisla pesh karta hun. mujhey maaf farma, wo gunah jo mainey kar liye hain aur jo abhi nahin kiye aur jo mainey khufiya kiye hain aur jo elania kiye hain. tu hi kisi ko aagey karney wala hai aur tu hi peechey karney wala hai. terey siwa koi mabood nahin aur Allah Taala ki madad key baghair na nuqsan sey bachney ka heela hai aur na faeyda hasil karney ki taqat."
1621,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney bataya ke eik raat main ummul-Mominin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) key yahan soyaa jo meri khaala thin. main bistar key chodaai mein let gaya jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki biwi mohtarma bistar ki lambai mein let gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) so gaey yahan tak ke jab raat nisf ho gaee ya maamuli kam o besh to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jaag uthey. aap apney haathon sey apna chehra miltey huye uth bethey, phir aap ney sura Aale-Imran ki aakhiri das aayaat tilawat farmaain, phir eik latkey huye mishkizey ki taraf uthey aur us sey wuzu farmaya aur behtareen wuzu farmaya, phir namaz padhney lagey. Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke main bhi utha aur mainey isi tarah kya jis tarah aap ney kya tha, phir main gaya aur aap key pehlu mein khada ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apna daayan haath merey sar par rakha aur mera daayan kaan pakad kar maroda. aap ney do rakatein padhin phir do, phir do, phir do, phir do, phir do, phir eik rakat padhi, phir let gaey yahan tak ke muazzan aap ko jamaat ki ittila deney aaya to aap ney do halki rakatein padhin"
1622,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey they to apney munh ko miswak key sath saaf kartey they.
1623,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko tahajjud padhney uthtey to apney munh mubarak ko miswak key sath saaf farmatey.
1624,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamen hukm diya jata tha ke jab hum raat ko uthen to miswak karen.
1625,Hazrat Shaqeeq bayan kartey hain ke hamen hukm diya jata tha ke jab hum raat ko uthen to apney munh miswak sey saaf karen.
1626,"Hazrat abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kis dua sey apni namaz ( tahajjud ) shuru farmatey they? unhoney farmaya : aap jab raat ko namaz key liye uthtey to ye dua padhtey : (اللھم رب جبریل . ۔ . الی صراط مستقیم) aey Allah ! Jibrael, mekael aur Israafeel key rab ! aasmano aur zaminon ko paida karney waley ! har ghaib o hazir ko janney waley! to apney bandon mein un chizon ka faisla kerega jin mein wo ikhtilaf kartey hain. aey Allah! mujhey us haq ki taraf raahnumai farma jis mein ikhtilaf kya gaya hai. yaqinan to jis ko chahta hai sidhey raastey par chala deta hai."
1627,"Hazrat Humed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf sey riwayat hai ke as-habe-Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mein sey eik sahabi ney kaha : main eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. mainey (dil mein) kaha : Allah ki qism ! main (raat ki ) namaz key waqt b-ghaur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekhunga taake mujhey pata chaley ke aap kya kartey hain. jab aap ney Isha ki namaz padh li to aap kafi raat tak letey rahey, phir aap jaagey aur ufaq mein dekha, phir aap ney ye aayat padhi : (ربنا ما خلقت ھذا باطلا) yahan tak ke aap ney (انک لا تخلف المیعاد) tak padha, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney bistar ki taraf jhukey aur is mein sey miswak nikali, phir aap ney apney paas padey huye chamdey key bartan sey eik piyaley mein kuch pani dala aur miswak farmaey, (aur wuzu kya.) phir aap ney namaz shuru farmaey. mera khayal hai aap jitni der soey they, utni der aap ney namaz padhi, phir aap let gaey yahan tak ke mera khayal hai ke aap itni der soey jitni der namaz padhi thi, phir jaagey aur isi tarah kya jis tarah pehley kya tha. aur wohi kuch padha jo pehli dafa padha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Fajr sey pehley teen baar aisey kya."
1628,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke agar hum chahtey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko raat mein namaz padhtey huye dekhen to dekh letey. aur agar hum chahtey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko soya huwa dekhen to ye bhi dekh letey.
1629,"ibn abi Muleka bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Yala bin Mamlak ney ummul-Mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz key mutalliq pucha to unhoney farmaya : aap Isha ki namaz padhtey they phir sunnatein padhtey they, phir uskey baad jitni raat tak Allah chahta aap namaz padha kartey, phir so rehtey itni der tak jitni der namaz padhi thi. phir jaagtey aur namaz padhtey itni der tak jitni der tak soey aur ye akheer ki namaz Fajr tak hoti."
1630,"Hazrat Yala bin Mamlak bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat key barey mein puchha (yani aap kalamullah kyonkar padhtey they) aur aap ki namaz key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : tumhen aap ki namaz sey kya sarokaar (yani tumhara poochhna be faeyda hai. kyonkey tum wesi namaz nahin padh saktey) aap namaz padhtey they phir so rehtey jitni der namaz padhi phir namaz padhtey jitni der soey they phir sotey jitni der namaz padhi hoti yahan tak ke subh ho jati, phir unhoney (Umme-Salma) ney aap ki qirat bayan farmaai to aisi qirat bayan farmaai jiska har har harf alag-alag samajh mein aata tha."
1631,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah azz-w-jall ko sab sey pyara roza Dawud alehissalam ka roza hai. wo eik din roza rakhtey they aur eik din chhodtey they. aur Allah Taala ko sab sey ziyada mehbub namaz Dawud alehissalam ki namaz hai. wo nisf raat sotey they, tihai raat namaz padhtey they aur phir raat ka chata hissa sotey they."
1632,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis raat mujhey Meraj karwai gaee, main eik surkh tiley key qarib Musa alehissalam key paas sey guzra. wo khadey apni qabr mein namaz padh rahey they."
1633,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main surkh tiley key qarib Musa alehissalam key paas sey guzra jabkey wo khadey namaz padh rahey they. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hamarey nazdik ye riwayat Muaz bin Khalid ki riwayat sey ziyada durust hai. «wallahu taala aalam»"
1634,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main Musa alehissalam ki qabr key paas sey guzra jabkey wo apni qabr mein namaz padh rahey they."
1635,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis raat mujhey Meraj karwai gaee, main Musa alehissalam key paas sey guzra jabkey wo apni qabr mein namaz padh rahey they."
1636,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jis raat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Meraj karwai gaee, aap Musa alehissalam key paas sey guzrey jabkey wo apni qabr mein namaz padh rahey they."
1637,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba mein sey eik sahabi ney khabar di ke jis raat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Meraj karwai gaee, aap Musa alehissalam key paas sey guzrey they jabkey wo apni qabr mein namaz padh rahey they."
1638,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key kisi sahabi sey riwayat ki hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis raat mujhey Meraj karwai gaee, mein Musa alehissalam key paas sey guzra jabkey wo apni qabr mein namaz padh rahey they."
1639,"Hazrat Khubab bin Arat (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, ye sahabi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath jange-Badr mein shareek huye they, unhoney eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko b-ghaur dekha ke aap sari raat namaz padhtey rahey, yahan tak ke Fajr ho gaee. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni namaz sey salam phera ( farigh huye ) to Khubab aap key paas hazir huye aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! merey maa baap aap par qurban! aaj raat aap ney itni namaz padhi hai ke mainey aap ko itni namaz padhtey nahin dekha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : han, ye raghbat aur rahbat (khofe-Ilaahi) wali namaz thi. mainey is mein apney rab taala sey teen chizon ka sawal kya tha. Allah Taala ney do cheezen de din, eik nahin di. mainey apney rab azz-w-jall sey sawal kya tha ke hamen un azabon sey halak na karey jin key sath pehli ummaton ko halak kya tha. Allah Taala ney meri ye baat maan li. doosra sawal ye tha ke hum par hamarey kafir dushmanon ko mukammal ghalba na dey. Allah Taala ney meri ye baat bhi maan li, phir mainey apney rab sey ye sawal kya ke hamen girohon aur firqon mein na baant dena. Allah Taala ney ye baat nahin maani."
1640,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jab Ramzanul-Mubarak ka aakhiri dahaka (das din) shuru hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sari raat jaagtey (ibadat kartey) aur apney ghar walon ko bhi jagaatey aur apna tehband kis letey.
1641,Hazrat abu-Is-haq bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Aswad bin Yazid key paas aaya aur arz kya. wo merey bhai aur dost they. aey abu-Amr! mujhey wo hadees bayan kijiye jo aap ko ummul-Mominin (Hazrat Aaisha Raziallahu anhu anha) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki (raat ki) namaz key barey mein bayan ki hai. unhoney kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat key shuru mein (Isha ki namaz key baad) so jatey they aur raat ka aakhiri hissa jaagtey (ibadat kartey) they.
1642,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main nahin jaanti ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kabhi eik raat mein sara Quran padha ho ya subh tak sari raat namaz padhi ho ya Ramzanul-Mubarak key ilawa kabhi purey mahiney key rozey rakhey hun.
1643,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik dafa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas tashrif laye jabkey unkey paas eik aurat bethi thi. aap ney farmaya : ye kon hai? mainey arz kya : falan aurat hai jo raat ko soti nahin. mainey uski namaz ka zikr kya. aap ney farmaya : rehney do. itna kaam ikhtiyar karo jiski tum (hamesha) taqat rakh sakti ho. Allah ki qasam! Allah Taala (sawab deney sey) nahin uktaaega. tum hi (neki karney sey) ukta jaogey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko wo deeni kaam ziyada achcha lagta tha jis par us kaam wala hameshgi kerey.
1644,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein dakhil huye to eik rassi do sutonon key darmiyan bandhi hui dekhi. aap ney puchha : ye rassi kaisi hai? logon ney kaha : (Ummul-Mominin ) Hazrat Zainab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ki hai. wo namaz padhti hain. jab thak jati hain to uska sahara leti hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey khol do. tum mein sey har shakhs us waqt tak namaz padhey jab tak is mein chusti baqi rahey. jab wo sust pad jaey to namaz chhod kar beth rahey.
1645,Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (nafl ) namaz itni lambi padhtey they ke aap key qadam mubarak sooj jatey they. aap sey guzarish ki gaee ke Allah Taala ney to aap key agley pichley sab qusur maaf farma diye hain (phir aap itni ibadat kyon kartey hain?) aap ney farmaya : kya main Allah Taala ka shukr-guzar banda na banu?
1646,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) is qadr lambi namaz padhtey they ke aap key qadam mubarak phat jatey they.
1647,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko bahut der tak namaz padhtey rehtey. jab aap khadey ho kar namaz shuru farmatey to rukoo bhi khadey ho kar hi farmatey aur jab beth kar namaz shuru farmatey to rukoo bhi beth kar hi farmatey.
1648,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kabhi khadey ho kar nafl namaz padhtey they aur kabhi beth kar. jab khadey ho kar namaz shuru farmatey to rukoo bhi khadey ho kar farmatey aur jab beth kar namaz shuru farmatey to rukoo bhi beth kar farmatey."
1649,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) beth kar namaz shuru farmatey to bethey bethey hi qirat farmatey. jab aap ki qirat sey tees ya chaalis aayaat baqi reh jatin to aap khadey ho jatey aur wo aayaat khadey ho kar tilawat farmatey phir rukoo farmatey phir sajda farmatey phir dusri rakat mein bhi aisey hi kartey.
1650,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko beth kar namaz padhtey nahin dekha yahan tak ke aap budhapey mein dakhil ho gaey, phir aap beth kar namaz shuru farmatey aur qirat kartey. jab is sura ki tees chaalis aayaat reh jatin to khadey ho kar unhein padhtey, phir rukoo farmatey."
1651,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (kabhi) qirat beth kar kartey. jab rukoo ka irada farmatey to itni der pehley khadey ho jatey jitni der mein insan chaalis aayaat padh sakta hai.
1652,"Hazrat Saad bin Hisham bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Madina Munawra aaya aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. unhoney puchha : to kon hai? mainey kaha : Hisham bin Aamir ka beta Saad hun. farmaney lagin : Allah Taala terey baap par reham farmaey. mainey arz kya : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki (raat ki nafl ) namaz key barey mein bataiye. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) to bahut buland o baala shakhsiyat they. mainey kaha : yaqinan aisa hi hai. farmaney lagin : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko Isha ki namaz padhtey, phir apney bistar par let kar so jatey. jab aadhi raat guzar jati to uth kar qazaey hajat kartey aur pani ley kar wuzu kartey, phir (apney ghar ki) masjid mein dakhil ho jatey aur aath rakaat padhtey mujhey yun mehsus hota tha ke aap un mein qirat, rukoo aur sajdey barabar kartey they, phir eik rakat padhtey aur uskey baad beth kar do rakat padhtey, phir let jatey, phir kabhi to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap key soney sey pehley hi aa kar namaz ki ittilaa kartey aur kabhi aap halki si neend ley letey they aur kabhi mujhey shak sa hota ke aap soey huye hain ya nahin yahan tak ke Bilal aa kar aap ko namaz ki ittilaa kartey. to ye thi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki raat ki namaz yahan tak ke aap ki umr badh gaee aur aap farba ho gaey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney aap key motapey key barey mein chand baaten zikr kin, phir unhoney farmaya : (us umr mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon ko Isha ki namaz padhatey, phir apney bistar par let jatey. jab nisf raat guzar jati to uthtey aur qazaey hajat kartey aur wuzu ka pani ley kar wuzu farmatey phir masjid ( ghar mein namaz key liye makhsus jagah ) main dakhil ho jatey aur chhe rakaat padhtey mujhey yun mehsus hota tha ke aap un mein qirat, rukoo aur sajda eik jaisa kartey they, phir eik rakat padhtey, phir beth kar do rakaat padhtey, phir let jatey. kabhi to Bilal aap key soney sey pehley hi aa kar namaz ki ittila kartey. kabhi aap halki si neend ley letey they aur kabhi mujhey shak rehta ke aap so gaey hain ya nahin, yahan tak ke Bilal aa kar aap ko namaz ki ittilaa kartey. ( wafat tak ) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki (raat ki ) namaz yehi rahi."
1653,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) rozey ki haalat mein merey chehrey (key bosey) sey perhez nahin farmatey they aur jab aap qaribul-wafat they to farz namaz key ilawa aap ki aksar namaz beth kar hoti thi. aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key nazdik zyada pasandida amal wo hota tha jis par insan hameshgi kerey, chahey wo thoda hi ho. Yunus ney is riwayat ko Abu-Is-haq sey bayan kartey huye umr bin abi zyada ki mukhalifat ki hai aur ye riwayat (عن ابی اسحاق an الاسود an ام سلمہ) ki sanad sey bayan ki hai."
1654,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni wafat key qarib farz namaz key ilawa namaz aksar beth kar padha kartey they. Shoba aur Sufiyan ney Yunus ki mukhalifat ki hai, unhoney ye riwayat (عن ابی اسحاق an الاسود an ام سلمہ) ki sanad sey bayan ki hai."
1655,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wafat key qarib farz namaz key ilawa baqi namaz aksar beth kar padha kartey they. aur aap key nazdik ziyada pasandida amal wo tha jis par hameshgi ki jaey bhaley hi wo kam ho.
1656,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wafat key qarib farz namaz key ilawa baqi namaz aksar beth kar padha kartey they. aur aap key nazdik pasandida amal wo tha jis par hameshgi ki jaey chahey wo kam ho. Usman bin Abu-Suleman ney un ki mukhalifat ki hai unhoney ye riwayat An abi Salma an Aaisha ki sanad sey bayan ki hai.
1657,Usman bin Abu Suleman (Alaihissalam) sey marwi hai ke abu-Salma ney un sey kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney un sey bayan farmaya ke wafat sey pehley Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni aksar namazon ko beth kar padhtey they.
1658,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaqeeq sey marwi hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( nafl ) namaz beth kar padhtey they? unhoney farmaya : han, jab logon ( ki fikr aur unkey kamon key bojh ) ney aap ko budha kar diya tha."
1659,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, farmati hain : mainey kabhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko beth kar nafl namaz padhtey nahin dekha tha yahan tak ke aap ki wafat sey eik saal qabl aisa huwa ke aap beth kar namaz padhney lagey, magar aap sura ko itna thahar thahar kar sukun sey padhtey they ke wo apney sey lambi sura sey bhi lambi ban jati thi."
1660,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko beth kar namaz padhtey dekha to mainey kaha : mujh sey to ye bayan kya gaya hai ke aap ney farmaya hai : beth kar namaz padhney waley ko khadey ho kar namaz padhney waley sey nisf sawab milta hai. ab aap beth kar namaz padh rahey hain? aap ney farmaya : baat sahih hai, magar main tum jaisa nahin."
1661,"Hazrat Imran bin Husein Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey beth kar ( nafl ) namaz padhney waley key barey mein puchha. aap ney farmaya : jo khada ho kar nafl namaz padhey to wo afzal ( ziyada sawab wala ) hai aur jo beth kar padhey, us ko khadey ho kar padhney waley sey nisf sawab milega aur jo let kar padhey, usey beth kar padhney waley sey bhi nisf sawab milega."
1662,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, farmati hain : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko chaar zanu beth kar namaz padhtey huye dekha. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke main nahin janta ke us hadees ko abu-Dawud (hafrii) ( mashhoor muhaddis nahin ) key ilawa kisi aur ney bayan kya hai. wo halanki suqa rawi hai magar mein samajhta hun, ye hadees khata hai. «wallah taala aalim » ."
1663,"Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Qais sey manqul hai, farmatey hain : mainey ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha ke raat ki nafl namaz mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat kaisey hoti thi ? buland aawaz sey ya aahista? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke aap dono tarah qirat farmaya kartey they, kabhi buland aawaz sey kabhi aahista ."
1664,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) apney shagirdon ko bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs buland aawaz sey Quran padhta hai, wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jo elaaniya sadqa karta hai aur jo shakhs aahista Quran padhta hai wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jo chupa kar sadqa karta hai."
1665,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey eik raat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (raat ki nafl ) namaz padhi. aap ney Sura Baqra shuru ki. mainey socha ke aap so aayaten padh kar rukoo farmaeyngey lekin aap aagey badh gaey. mainey socha ke aap do so aayaten padh kar rukoo farmaeyngey lekin aap aagey guzar gaey. mainey socha, puri sura eik rakat mein padhengey lekin aap padhtey gaey aur Sura Nisa shuru kar di aur puri padh dali, phir Ale-Imran shuru kar di aur khatam kar dali. padhtey bhi thehar thehar kar they. jab kisi aisi aayat par aatey jis mein tasbih ka zikr hota to tasbih padhtey aur jab koi sawal wali aayat padhtey to ruk kar Allah Taala sey wo chiz maangtey aur jab koi aisi aayat padhtey jis mein panah wali chiz ka zikr hota to us chiz sey Allah Taala ki panah talab kartey, phir rukoo farmaya aur ( subhan rabbiyal azeem ) padhtey rehtey. aap ka rukoo taqriban aap key qiyam key barabar tha, phir sar uthaya aur kaha : ( Samiallahu liman hamida ) aap ka ye qauma bhi taqriban rukoo key barabar tha, phir sajda farmaya aur ( subhan rabbiyal-aala ) padhtey rahey to aap ka sajda aap key rukoo key qarib tha."
1666,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Ramzanul-Mubarak mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath ( tahajjud ki ) namaz padhi. aap ney rukoo farmaya aur rukoo mein itni der ( subhan rabbiyal azeem ) padhtey rahey jitni der qiyam farmaya tha, phir ( sajdey key baad ) bethey, itni der  (رب اغفرلی ! رب اغفرلی) aey merey rab ! mujhey maaf farma, aey merey rab ! mujhey maaf farma. kehtey rahey, jitni der qiyam farmaya tha, phir sajda farmaya to itni der ( subhana rabiyal Aala) kehtey rahey, jitni der khadey rahey they. is tarah aap ney sirf chaar rakaat padhin ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) subh ki namaz ki ittila deney aa gaey. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees merey nazdik mursal hai. mein nahin janta ke Talha bin Yazid ney Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey koi riwayat suni ho. Ala bin Musaiyab key ilawa dusrey raawiyon ney Talha aur Hazrat Huzefa key darmiyan eik aadmi ka wasta zikr kya hai."
1667,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : din aur raat ki ( nafl ) namaz do do rakat kar key padhnii chahiye. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain merey nazdik ye hadees khata hai. « wallahu-aalam » ."
1668,Hazrat Taoos Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bayan farmatey hain ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey raat ki namaz ka tariqa puchha to aap ney farmaya : do do kar key padhtey jao. jab tujhey subh ka khatra ho to eik rakat padh lo.
1669,Hazrat Salim apney walid ( ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma) sey bayan farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai. jab tujhey subh key tulu honey ka khatra ho to ( subh tulu honey sey pehley) eik rakat padh ley.
1670,Hazrat abu-Salma Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko member par ye farmatey suna jabkey aap sey raat ki namaz key barey mein puchha gaya tha. (aap ney farmaya : ) do do kar key padho. jab subh ka khatra ho to eik rakat padh lo.
1671,Hazrat Naafey bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney hum ko bataya ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey raat ki namaz key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : do do kar key padhi jaey. jab kisi ko subh key tulu honey ka dar ho to eik rakat padh ley.
1672,Hazrat Naafey Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai. jab tujhey subh ka khadsha ho to eik rakat padh ley.
1673,Hazrat Salim Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bayan kartey hain ke musalmanon mein sey eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : raat ki namaz kaisey padhi jaey ? to aap ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do rakat padhi jaey. jab tujhey subh key tulu ka qurb mehsus ho to eik rakat padh ley.
1674,Hazrat Humed bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney bataya ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey raat ki namaz ( tahajjud ) key barey mein puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai. jab tujhey subh tulu honey ka khatra ho to eik rakat padh ley.
1675,Hazrat Salim aur Humed dono ney Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bayan kya ke eik aadmi ney uth kar kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! raat ki namaz ( padhney ka tariqa ) kya hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do kar key padho. jab subh ka dar ho to eik rakat padh lo.
1676,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz witr padhi, phir aap ney farmaya : aey Quran walo ! witr padha karo kyonkey Allah Taala witr ( akela ) hai aur witr ko pasand farmata hai."
1677,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke witr ki namaz farz namaz ki tarah wajib nahin balke ye sunnat (muakkada) hai jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumharey liye jari farmaya hai.
1678,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke merey dili mehbub Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey teen baaton ki nasihat takeed key sath ki hai : main witr padh kar soun, har mahiney mein teen rozey rakhun aur Fajr (ya zuha) ki do rakaaton ki pabandi karun."
1679,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey merey dili mehbub (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen baaton ki takeed farmaai ke shuru raat mein witr padh liya karun, Fajr ki sunnaton ki pabandi karun aur har mahiney mein teen nafli rozey rakhun."
1680,"Hazrat Qais bin Talaq sey riwayat hai ke merey walid mohtaram Hazrat Talaq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Ramzanul-Mubarak main eik din hum sey milney key liye tashrif laye. unhein Sham ho gaee. us raat unhoney hamen namaz padhaai aur witr padhaaey, phir masjid mein tashrif ley gaey aur apney dusrey sathiyon ko namaz padhaai, yahan tak ke jab witr baqi reh gaey to eik aadmi ko apni jagah aagey kya aur farmaya : tum unhein witr padha do ( kyonkey mein padh chuka hun. ) mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai ke eik raat mein do dafa witr nahin padhey ja saktey."
1681,"Hazrat Aswad bin Yazid sey manqul hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki (raat ki ) namaz key mutalliq puchha to unhoney farmaya : aap shuru raat ( yani namaz Isha key baad ) so jatey they, phir jaagtey (aur namaz padhtey ), phir subh qarib hoti to witr padhtey, phir apney bistar par tashrif ley aatey. agar aap ko zarurat mehsus hoti to apni biwi sey jima kartey, phir jab Azan suntey to fauran uth khadey hotey agar junbi hotey to ghusl farmatey wagarna wuzu kartey. (sunnatein padhtey) aur namaz key liye masjid mein chaley jatey."
1682,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney witr awwal raat mein bhi padhey, darmiyan raat mein bhi aur aakhir raat mein bhi. aakhiri umr mein aap key witr aakhir raat mein (Fajr sey pehley) hotey they."
1683,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke jo shakhs raat ko nafl namaz padhey to wo witr aakhir mein padhey kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us ka hukm detey they.
1684,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey witr key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : subh sey pehley witr padh lo.
1685,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Fajr tulu honey sey pehley witr padh liya karo."
1686,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Muntashir sey marwi hai ke main Hazrat Amr bin Shurehbil ki masjid mein tha, namaz ki takbir ho gaee ( magar wo na aaye. ) log unka intizar karney lagey, phir wo aaye to unhoney kaha : main witr padh raha tha, neez unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha gaya : kya subh ki Azan key baad witr padhey ja saktey hain? unhoney farmaya : han, balke iqaamat key baad bhi, phir unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka waqia bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz Fajr sotey mein reh gaee thi yahan tak ke suraj tulu ho gaya to aap ney us waqt namaz padhi."
1687,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sawari par witr padh liya kartey they.
1688,Hazrat Naafey sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma apney oont par witr padh liya kartey they aur wo bayan farmatey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi aisey kya kartey they.
1689,Hazrat Saeed bin Yasar ney kaha ke mujhey Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) oont par witr padh liya kartey they.
1690,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : witr aakhir raat main eik rakat hai."
1691,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : witr aakhir raat main eik rakat padha jaey."
1692,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke eik badwi shakhs ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey raat ki namaz key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : do do rakat kar key padhtey jao aur aakhir raat main eik rakat witr padh lo.
1693,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do rakat kar key padho. jab tumhara irada namaz khatam karney ka ho to eik rakat padh lo. ye rakat tumhari padhi hui puri namaz ko witr bana degi"
1694,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai. aur witr ( aakhir mein) eik rakat hai."
1695,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey raat ki namaz key barey mein puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai. jab tum mein sey kisi ko subh key tulu honey ka khadsha ho to eik rakat padh ley. ye uski sari namaz ko witr bana degi.
1696,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai. jab tumhein tulu subh ka khatra ho to eik rakat witr padh lo.
1697,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko giyara rakaat padhtey they. un mein sey eik rakat alag witr padhtey, phir apney daeyn pehlu par let jatey."
1698,"Hazrat abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman sey manqul hai, unhoney ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha ke Ramzanul-Mubarak mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki (raat ki ) namaz kaisey hoti thi ? to unhoney farmaya : aap Ramzan ya ghair Ramzan mein ( umuman ) giyara rakaat sey zayed nahin padhtey they. chaar rakaat padhtey aisi khoobsurat aur taweel ke kuch na pooch, phir chaar padhtey aisi khoobsurat aur taweel ke kuch na poochh, phir teen rakaat padhtey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aap witr ( teen rakaat ) padhney sey pehley so jatey hain? aap ney farmaya : aey Aaisha ! meri aankhen soti hain, dil nahin sota."
1699,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr ki do rakaaton key baad salam nahin phertey they.
1700,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) teen rakaat witr padhtey pehli rakat mein Sura Sura Aala dusri mein Sura Kafirun aur teesri mein Sura Ikhlas padhtey they. aur rukoo sey pehley qunoot padhtey they, phir jab farigh hotey to faraaghat key waqt teen dafa سبحان الملک القدوس pak hai badshah nihayat padhi. padhtey aakhiri martaba lamba kar key padhtey they."
1701,Hazrat Ubai bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr ki pehli rakat mein Sura Aala dusri mein Sura Kafirun aur teesri mein Sura Ikhlas padhtey they.
1702,Hazrat Ubai bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr ( ki pehli rakat ) main Sura Aala dusri mein Sura Kafirun aur teesri mein Sura Ikhlas padha kartey they aur salam aakhir hi mein phertey they. aur salam key baad teen dafa سبحان الملک القدوس padhtey
1703,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) teen witr padhtey they. pehli rakat mein Sura Aala dusri mein Sura Kafirun aur teesri mein Sura Ikhlas padhtey they. zuhair ( bin Muawiya ) ney usey maqoof bayan kya hai.
1704,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma teen witr padha kartey they aur un mein Sura Aala , Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padhtey they."
1705,"Muhammad bin Ali apney baap Ali sey aur wo apney dada Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko ( tahajjud key liye) uthey aur miswak ki, phir ( wuzu key baad ) do rakatein padhin phir so gaey, phir uthey, miswak ki, wuzu farmaya aur do rakatein padhin yahan tak ke (us tarah ) chhe rakatein padhin phir teen witr padhey aur phir do rakatein padhein"
1706,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke main (eik raat ) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key yahan thehra huwa tha. aap uthey , wuzu kya aur miswak farmaai aur aap ye aayat padh rahey they : ان فی خلق السموت والارض واختلف الیل والنھار لایت لاولی الالبب yaqinan aasmano aur zamin ki takhleeq aur raat aur din key adal badal mein aql mand logon key liye nishaniyan hain. yahan tak ke aap un aayaat sey farigh huye, phir aap ney do rakatein padhin phir dobara so gaey, yahan tak ke mainey aap key kharratey suney, phir uthey aur miswak o wuzu farmaya, phir do rakatein padhin phir so gaey, phir uthey. wuzu kya, miswak farmatey aur do rakatein padhin phir teen witr padhey."
1707,"Muhammad bin Ali Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jaagey aur miswak ki, phir raawi ney puri hadees bayan ki."
1708,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko aath rakatein padhtey aur teen witr padhtey, phir Fajr ki namaz sey pehley ( Fajr ki sunnatein ) do rakat padhtey Amr bin Murra ney Habib bin abi sabit ki mukhalifat ki hai aur عن یحیی بن الجزار an ام سلمۃ رضی اللہ عنہا kaha hai. ( jabkey Habib bin abi sabit ney « an ام سلمۃ » key bajaey « an ibne-Abbas » kaha tha. )"
1709,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko tera rakat padhtey they, phir jab aap boodhey aur kamzor ho gaey to no padhney lagey. Ammara bin Umer ney ( Amr bin Murra ki ) mukhalifat ki hai aur ye riwayat عن یحیی بن الجزار an عائشۃ ki sanad sey bayan ki hai. ( jabkey Amr bin Murra ney « an عائشۃ » key bajaey « an Umme-Salma » kaha tha. )"
1710,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko no rakat padhtey they. jab aap boodhey aur bojhal ho gaey to saat padhney lagey.
1711,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : witr haq hai jo chahey saat padh ley, jo chahey paanch padh ley, jo chahey teen padh ley aur jo chahey eik padh ley."
1712,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : witr haq hai jo shakhs paanch witr padhna chahey, paanch padh ley, jo teen padhna chahey teen padh ley aur jo eik padhna chahey eik padh ley."
1713,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke witr haq hai. jo shakhs paanch witr padhna chahey, paanch padh ley, jo teen padhna chahey teen padh ley aur jo eik padhna chahey eik padh ley."
1714,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jo shakhs chahey saat witr padh ley, jo shakhs chahey paanch witr padh ley, jo shakhs chahey teen witr padh ley aur jo shakhs chahey eik witr padh ley. aur jo shakhs chahey (yani majbur ho) wo isharay sey padh ley."
1715,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) paanch ya saat witr padhtey to darmiyan mein na salam phertey they aur na kalam farmatey they."
1716,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) saat ya paanch witr padhtey to darmiyan mein salam nahin phertey they."
1717,"Hazrat Hakam Hazrat Muqsim sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : witr saat hain aur paanch sey kam to qatan nahin. mainey ye baat Hazrat Ibrahim Nakhai sey zikr ki to unhoney kaha : muqsim ney ye baat kis sey naqal ki hai? mainey kaha : mujhey to ilm nahin. hukm kehtey hain : main Haj key liye gaya to muqsim sey mila aur un sey puchha ke wo riwayat aap kis sey bayan kartey hain? wo kehney lagey : suqa aur moatabar ashkhas sey. Hazrat Aaisha aur Hazrat Memuna Raziallahu anhuma sey."
1718,Hazrat Aaisha Raziallahu anha sey manqul hai ki Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) paanch witr padhtey they aur sirf aakhiri rakat mein ( tashahud key liye) bethtey they.
1719,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) boodhey aur farba ho gaey to aap saat witr padhtey they. aakhiri key siwa kisi rakat mein (tashahud key liye) na bethtey they. aur salam pherney key baad beth kar do rakaat padhtey they. to ye nau rakaat ho gaeen aey beta ! aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab koi nafl namaz shuru kar letey they to is par hameshgi ko pasand farmatey they. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai. Hisham Dustwaai ney is riwayat mein Shoba ki mukhalifat ki hai.
1720,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab nau rakat witr padhtey to (tashahud key liye) aathwin rakat sey pehley kisi rakat mein na bethtey they. aathwin mein beth kar Allah Taala ki hamd aur us ka zikr farmatey aur duayen kartey (yani tashahud padhtey) phir salam pherey baghair uth khadey hotey, phir naween rakat padh kar bethtey aur Allah Taala ka zikr farmatey aur duayen kartey, phir itni aawaz sey salam phertey ke hamein sunai deta tha, phir beth kar do rakaat padhtey, phir jab boodhey aur kamzor ho gaey to saat rakaat padhtey they aur chhatti key siwa kisi rakat mein (tashahud key liye) na bethtey phir (chhatti mein beth kar) uth khadey hotey aur salam na phertey phir saatwin padh kar bethtey phir salam phertey phir beth kar do rakat padhtey."
1721,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye aap ki miswak aur wuzu ka pani tayyar rakhtey they, phir jab Allah Taala pasand farmata raat mein aap ko utha deta. aap (uth kar) miswak aur wuzu farmatey aur no rakaat is tarah padhtey ke un mein sey kisi key aakhir mein na bethtey magar aathwin rakat par bethtey. Allah ki hamd kartey aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par durood padhtey aur duayen kartey magar salam na phertey, phir naween (rakat) padh kar bethtey aur Allah ki hamd aur sanaa farmatey aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par durood padhtey aur duayen kartey phir itni aawaz sey salam kehtey ke hamein sunai deta phir beth kar do rakaten padhtey."
1722,"Hazrat Zarara bin Oofaa sey manqul hai, farmatey hain : jab Hazrat Saad bin Hisham bin Aamir hamarey paas aaye to unhoney hamein bataya : main Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key paas gaya aur un sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki witr namaz key barey mein puchha. wo farmaney lagey : kya main tumhein aisi shakhsiyat na bataun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki witr namaz ko roey arz par basney waley tamam logon sey ziyada jaanti hain? mainey kaha : kon? farmaya : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (kyonkey wo aap ki biwi thin aur aap ki khilwat (tanhaai) ki sathi thin). hum wahan gaey, unhein salam kaha, un (Hazrat Aaisha Raziallahu anhu ) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur un sey sawal kiya. mainey kaha : hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki witr ki namaz key barey mein bataiye. farmaney lagin : hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye aap ki miswak aur wuzu ka pani tayyar rakhtey they. raat ko jis waqt Allah Taala chahta aap ko jagaa deta. aap miswak aur wuzu farmatey phir nau rakatin is tarah padhtey ke aathwin rakat key ilawa kisi rakat mein tashahud key liye na bethtey. (aathwein rakat mein beth kar) Allah Taala ki hamd aur zikr farmatey aur duayen padhtey, phir baghair salam key uth khadey hotey aur naween rakat padh kar bethtey aur Allah Taala ki hamd aur zikr farmatey aur duayen padhtey, phir itni aawaz sey salam phertey ke hamein sunai deta phir beth kar do rakat padhtey to ye giyara rakaat ho gaeen aey betey ! phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) boodhey ho gaey aur aap ko gosht ney pakad liya (aap farba ho gaey) to saat rakaat padh kar salam phertey aur beth kar do rakaat padhtey to aey beta ! ye nau ho gaeen. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab koi namaz shuru farma letey to is par hameshgi aur pabandi ko pasand farmatey they."
1723,"Hazrat Saad bin Hisham sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko farmatey suna : tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) nau rakaat witr padh kar, phir bethey bethey do rakat padhtey aur jab kamzor ho gaey to saat rakaat witr padhtey, phir bethey bethey do rakat padhtey."
1724,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) nau rakaat witr padhtey, phir beth kar do rakat padhtey."
1725,"Hazrat Saad bin Hisham sey manqul hai ke main Ummul-Mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaya aur un sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki raat ki namaz key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : aap raat ko aath rakaat padhtey, phir naween rakat witr padhtey aur beth kar do rakaten padhtey ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
1726,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko (nafl namaz) nau rakat padha kartey they.
1727,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) raat ko giyara rakat padhtey they aur un mein sey eik rakat (alag) witr padhtey, phir apney daeyn pehlu par let jatey."
1728,Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tehra rakat witr padhtey they. jab boodhey aur kamzor ho gaey to nau rakaat witr padhney lagey.
1729,"Hazrat Abu-Mujliz sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) (safar key dauraan mein) Makka aur Madina key darmiyan they to unhoney Isha ki namaz do rakat padhi, phir khadey huye aur eik rakat witr padha aur is mein Sura Nisa ki sau aayaat padhin phir farmaya : mainey is baat mein zarra bhar kotahi nahin ki ke wahan paon rakhun jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney qadam mubarak rakhey aur wohi kuchh padhun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney padha."
1730,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr ki namaz mein Sura-Aala, Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padha kartey they aur jab salam phertey they to teen dafa (سبحان الملک القدوس) padhtey."
1731,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witron mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas (suraten) padha kartey they. Husain ney Zubaida aur Talha ki mukhalifat ki hai aur is riwayat ko (عن ذر an ابن عبدالرحمن بن ابزی an ابیہ an النبی ﷺ) ki sanad sey bayan kiya hai."
1732,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr namaz mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padha kartey they."
1733,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr namaz mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas (suraten) padha kartey they. aur jab salam phertey to teen dafa سبحان الملک القدوس kehtey aur teesri dafa apni aawaz ko mazeed ooncha kar detey they."
1734,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witron mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padha kartey they, phir jab salam phertey to (teen dafa) سبحان الملک القدوس farmatey aur teesri dafa سبحان الملک القدوس mazeed buland aawaz sey ada farmatey. is riwayat ko Mansoor ney Salma bin Kuheil sey bayan kiya hai aur (Hadees key raawi) Zar ka zikr nahin kiya."
1735,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr ki namaz mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padha kartey they aur jab jab salam pher kar farigh hotey to teen dafa سبحان الملک القدوس farmatey aur teesri dafa aawaz lambi kar detey. is riwayat ko Abdul-Malik bin Abu Suleman (Alaihissalam) ney Zubaida sey bayan kiya hai. unhoney bhi (Hadees key raawi) Zarr ka zikr nahin kiya."
1736,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr ki namaz mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padha kartey they. is riwayat ko Muhammad bin Juhaada ney bhi Zubaida sey bayan kiya hai. unhoney bhi (Hadees key raawi) Zarr ka zikr nahin kya."
1737,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witron mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padhtey they aur jab namaz sey farigh hotey to teen dafa سبحان الملک القدوس padhtey."
1738,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr namaz mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padhtey they."
1739,ye riwayat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa key betey sey unkey wastey key baghair yani mursal bhi aai hai. aur Ata bin Saaib ney Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa sey aur unhoney apney baap (Abdur-Rehman) sey ye riwayat bayan ki hai.
1740,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padhtey they."
1741,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas key sath witr padha kartey they, phir jab farigh hotey to teen dafa سبحان الملک القدوس padhtey."
1742,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key barey mein bayan farmatey hain ke aap Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas key sath witr padha kartey they, phir jab farigh hotey to teen dafa سبحان الملک القدوس padhtey aur teesri dafa aawaz khinchtey (lambi kartey) they."
1743,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr mein Sura (Aala) padhtey they. (Shoba key shagrid) Shaaba ney dono (Abu-Daawood aur Muhammad) ki mukhalifat ki hai aur is riwayat ko (شعبۃ an قتادۃ an زرارۃ بن اوفی an عمران بن حصین) ki sanad sey zikr kiya hai.
1744,Hazrat Imran bin Husain Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Sura (Aala) key sath witr padha. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke main nahin janta ke kisi raawi ney is riwayat mein Shaaba ki muwaafiqat ki ho. Yahya bin Saeed ney Shaaba ki mukhalifat ki hai.
1745,Hazrat Imran bin Husein Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ki namaz padhaai. (aap key peechhey) eik aadmi ney Sura (Aala) (halki aawaz key sath) padhi. jab aap namaz sey farigh huye to farmaya : Sura (Aala) kis ney padhi? eik aadmi ney kaha : mainey. aap ney farmaya : mujhey malum ho raha tha ke koi shakhs mujhey ishtabah (shak) mein dal raha hai.
1746,"Hazrat Husain (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuchh kalimaat sikhlaey jinhein main qunoot witr mein padha karta hun, ( اللھم اھدنی فیمن ھدیت . ۔ . تبارکت ربنا وتعالیت ),''aey Allah ! mujhey hidayat dey un logon mein shamil farma kar jin ko tu ney hidayat di. aur mujhey aafiyat di un logon mein shamil farma kar jin ko tu ney aafiyat di hai. mera wali ban ja un logon mein shamil farma kar jin ka to wali bana. aur merey liye un chizon mein barkat farma jo tu ney ata farmaeen. aur mujhey us faisley key shar sey bacha jo tu ney farma rakha hai. yaqinan to faisley karta hai aur terey khilaf faisla nahin kiya ja sakta. aur yaqinan wo shakhs zaleel nahin ho sakta jis ka to wali ho. aey hamarey Rab ! to bada ba-barkat aur buland aur baala hai."
1747,"Hazrat Husain bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye kalimaat witr mein padhney key liye sikhaey. farmaya : ke (اللھم ! اھدنی فیمن ھدیت . ۔ . وصلی اللہ Ali (Raziallahu anhu) النبی محمد),''aey Allah ! mujhey raahe-raast par chala un logon mein shamil farma kar jin ko tu ney raahe raast par chalaya aur chalaaey rakha. aur mujhey aafiyat ata farma un logon mein shamil farma kar jin ko tu ney aafiyat di. aur mera wali ho un logon mein shamil farma kar jin ka to wali huwa. aur merey liye un chizon mein barkat farma jo tu ney ata farmaeen. aur mujhey us faisley key shar aur nuqsan sey bacha jo tu ney farmaya kyonkey to (jo chahey) faisley farmata hai lekin terey khilaf faisla nahin kiya ja sakta. aur bilashuba wo shakhs zaleel nahin ho sakta jis ka to wali ho. aey hamarey Rab ! to ba-barkat aur buland aur baala hai. aur Allah Taala Nabi Karim Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par rahmatein farmaey."
1748,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni witr namaz key aakhir mein ye alfaz padhtey they : (اللھم انی اعوذ برضاک من سخطک . ۔ . انت کما اثنیت Ali (Raziallahu anhu) نفسک),''aey Allah ! main terey ghussey sey bachney key liye teri raza mandi ki panah chahta hun aur teri saza sey bachney key liye teri maafi aur aafiyat ki panah chahta hun aur main tujh sey dartey huye teri hi panah chahta hun. main teri mukammal tareef nahin kar sakta. to isi tarah hai jis tarah tu ney khud apni tareef ki hai."
1749,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) istisqaa (barish ki dua) key ilawa kisi bhi dua mein haath nahin uthatey they. (Hadees key raawi) Shoba ney kaha ke mainey (apney ustaad) Sabit (Banaani) sey kaha : kya aap ney ye riwayat khud Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey suni hai? unhoney kaha : (Subhan Allah !) mainey phir kaha : aap ney un sey suni hai? unhoney phir kaha : (Subhan Allah) (yani kya baghair suney bayan kar raha hun)?
1750,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Isha ki namaz sey farigh honey key baad Fajr tak raat mein Fajr ki do sunnaton key ilawa giyara rakat padha kartey they aur aap itna lamba sajda kartey they ke tum mein sey eik shakhs pachas aayaat padh sakta tha.
1751,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr ki namaz mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padha kartey they aur salam pherney key baad teen dafa buland aawaz sey سبحان الملک القدوس padhtey they."
1752,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas key sath witr padhtey they aur salam key baad teen dafa buland aawaz sey سبحان الملک القدوس farmatey they. Abu Nuaim ney un dono (Qaasim aur Muhammad bin Ubaid) ki mukhalifat ki hai aur is riwayat ko (AnSufiyan An Zubaida An Zarr An Saeed) ki sanad sey bayan kiya hai."
1753,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witron mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padhtey they, phir jab salam pherney key baad uthney ka irada farmatey to teen dafa buland aawaz sey سبحان الملک القدوس padhtey.Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hamarey nazdik Abu Nuaim, Muhammad bin Ubaid aur Imam Qasim bin Yazid sey ziyada bharosemand aur moatabar hain. hamarey nazdik Sufiyan Sooraa key shagrid is hadees mein saqaahat key lihaz sey ye tarteeb rakhtey hain. Yahya bin Saeed Qataan, Abdullah bin Mubarak, Wakeea bin Jarraah, Abdur-Rehman bin Mahdi, Abu Nuaim aur Aswad (wallahu-aalam). Jareer bin Haazim ney bhi Is hadees ko Zubaida sey bayan kiya hai. unhoney yun kaha hai : teesri dafa aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni aawaz ko lamba bhi kiya aur buland bhi."
1754,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr namaz mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padhtey they. aur jab salam phertey to teen dafa سبحان الملک القدوس farmatey aur teesri dafa apni aawaz ko khinchtey they aur mazeed buland farmatey they."
1755,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr ki namaz mein Sura (Aala), Sura Kafirun aur Sura Ikhlas padha kartey they aur jab farigh hotey to سبحان الملک القدوس kehtey. (Qatada key shagrid) Hisham ney is riwayat ko mursal bayan kiya hai. (yani baraahe-raast Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kiya hai. is mein Sahabi Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa ka zikr nahin kiya.)"
1756,Hazrat Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abzaa sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) witr (mein ye teen suraten) padhtey they. . ۔ phir raawi ney puri hadees bayan ki.
1757,"Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki raat ki namaz key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : aap kul tehra rakaat padhtey they. nau rakaten khadey ho kar jin main eik rakat witr hoti thi. do rakaten beth kar. jab rukoo ka irada farmatey to khadey ho jatey aur rukoo aur sajdey kartey. aisa aap witr key baad kartey they, phir jab subah ki Azan suntey to uthtey aur do halki rakaten padhtey."
1758,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zohar sey qabl chaar rakat (sunnatte muakada) aur Fajr sey qabl do rakat sunnat nahin chhodtey they. ye hadees bayan karney waley Shoba key dusrey shagirdon ney Usman bin umr ki mukhalifat ki hai, yani unhoney (Muhammad bin Muntashir aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key darmiyan) Masruq ka zikr nahin kiya."
1759,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zohar sey pehley chaar rakat aur Fajr sey pehley do rakat (sunnat) nahin chhodtey they. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hamarey nazdik ye riwayat durust hai aur Usman bin umr ki riwayat ghalat hai (wallahu-aalam). (is ki wazahat pehley ho chuki hai ke is riwayat mein Masruq ka zikr durust nahin.)
1760,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Fajr ki do sunnaten duniya aur uski har chiz sey behtar hain.
1761,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke jab subah ki Azan hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farz namaz key liye janey sey pehley do halki rakaten padha kartey they.
1762,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke jab Fajr achchhi tarah roshan ho jati to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) do rakaten padha kartey they.
1763,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jab muazzan Fajr ki namaz ki Azan sey farigh hota to Fajr wazeh aur roshan honey key baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uthtey aur Fajr ki farz namaz sey pehley do halki rakaten padhtey, phir apney daeyn pehlu par let jatey."
1764,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : to falan shakhs ki tarah na ho jana jo pehley raat ko (nafl) namaz padha karta tha phir us ney usey chhod diya.
1765,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Abdullah ! falan shakhs ki tarah na ho jana jo raat ka qiyam (nafl namaz) padha karta tha, phir us ney qiyamullail chhod diya."
1766,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki do halki rakaten padhtey they.
1767,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subah ki Azan aur iqaamat key darmiyan do halki rakaten padhtey they. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hamarey nazdik ye dono riwaayatein ghalat hain. (wallahu-aalam).
1768,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki Azan aur namaz key darmiyan do halki rakaten padhtey they.
1769,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Azan aur iqaamat key darmiyan Fajr ki do halki rakaten padhtey they.
1770,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subah ki namaz ki Azan aur iqaamat key darmiyan do halki rakaten padhtey they.
1771,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subah (ki namaz) sey pehley do rakaten padhtey they.
1772,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) batati hain ke jab subah ki namaz ki Azan hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subah ki namaz sey pehley do rakatein padha kartey they.
1773,Ummul-Mominin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jab muazzan (Azan keh kar) khamosh hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) do halki rakaten padhtey they.
1774,Mominon ki maa Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney batlaya : jab muazzan subah ki Azan keh kar khamosh hota aur subah zahir ho jati to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) subah ki namaz ki iqaamat sey pehley do halki rakaten padhtey they.
1775,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain ke mujh sey meri behan Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan kiya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki namaz sey pehley do halki rakaten padha kartey they.
1776,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke jab Fajr tulu hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) do rakaten padhtey they.
1777,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke jab Fajr tulu hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sirf do halki rakaten padhtey they.
1778,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke jab subah ki namaz ki Azan hoti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farz namaz ko janey sey pehley do halki rakaten padhtey they. ye riwayat Hazrat Salim ney bhi (Hazrat Naafey key bajaey ) (ibne-Umar an Hafsaa) ki sanad sey bayan ki hai.
1779,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki namaz sey pehley do rakaten padha kartey they. aur ye (kaam) Fajr tulu honey key baad hota tha (yani do rakaaton ki adaegi).
1780,Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney bataya ke jab Fajr roshan ho jati to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) do rakaten padhtey they.
1781,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki namaz ki Azan aur iqaamat key darmiyan do halki rakaten padha kartey they.
1782,"Hazrat Abu-Salma sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki raat ki namaz key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tehra rakaat padhtey they. pehley aath rakaat padhtey, phir witr (eik rakat) padhtey, phir beth kar do padhtey lekin jab rukoo ka irada farmatey to khadey ho kar rukoo farmatey. aur do rakaten subah ki Azan aur iqaamat key darmiyan padhtey they."
1783,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab subah ki Azan suntey to Fajr ki do sunnatein padhtey aur unhein halka padhtey they. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees munkir hai.
1784,Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas Hazrat Shureh Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : wo Quran ko sarhaana nahin banata.
1785,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke unhein unkey nazdik pasandida shakhs ney bataya ke in ko Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ko raat ko nafl namaz padhney ki aadat ho, phir kisi din is par neend ghalib aa jaey (aur wo nafl namaz na padh sakey) to Allah Taala (us din bhi) is (mamool ki) namaz ka ajr uskey liye likh deta hai aur uski neend uskey liye (Allah taala ki taraf sey) sadqa ban jati hai."
1786,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis aadmi ki koi muqarrar shuda namaz ho jisey wo laziman raat ko padhta ho lekin kisi din (ittifaaq se) wo soyaa raha (aur usey na padh saka) to neend uskey liye sadqa hogi jo Allah Taala ney is par kiya hai aur wo uskey liye uski (muqarrara) namaz ka sawab likheyga."
1787,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir isi tarah bayan kya jaisey pehley bayan huwa hai. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke is hadees ki sanad mein eik raawi Abu-Jafar Raazi hai jo ilm hadees mein qawi aur moatabar nahin."
1788,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai aur wo isey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunchatey they, aap ney farmaya : jo aadmi bistar par let'tey waqt niyat rakhta ho ke raat ko (namaz tahajjud key liye) utheyga lekin usey gehri neend aa gaee aur wo subah tak soyaa raha to uskey liye us namaz ka sawab likha jaeyga jiski us ney niyat ki aur uski neend uskey Rab ki taraf sey is par nawazish hogi. Sufiyan ney is riwayat mein Habib bin Abi Sabit ki mukhalifat ki hai."
1789,Sufiyan Sauri ney us riwayat ko Hazrat Abu-Zar aur Hazrat Abu-Darda Raziallahu anhuma ka apna qol (yani maqoof) bayan kiya hai.
1790,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko nafl namaz na padh saktey, yani neend ya takleef ka ghalba ho jata to din ko baara rakaat padhtey."
1791,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs raat ko apni muqarrar shuda mukammal ya kuchh namaz sey soyaa raha (na padh saka) phir wo usey Fajr ki namaz (tulu shams) sey namaze Zohar tak padh ley to us ka sawab yun likha jaeyga goya us ney raat ko padhi."
1792,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs raat ko apni mamool ki mukammal ya kuchh nafl namaz sey soyaa raha, phir us ney usey subah ki namaz (ka waqt khatam honey aur makrooh waqt guzarney key baad) sey Zohar ki namaz tak padh liya to yun samjho, us ney raat hi ko padhi."
1793,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jis shakhs sey raat ki muqarrara (nafl) namaz reh gaee aur us ney zawal shams (suraj) sey ley kar Zohar ki namaz tak padh li to yun samjho ke wo namaz us sey nahin rahi balke goya us ney bar-waqt padh li. Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) key betey Humed ney isey maqoof bayan kiya hai.
1794,"Hazrat Humed bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke jis aadmi ka raat ka muqarrar wird (zikr, Quran ya namaz) reh jaey to wo isey Zohar ki namaz sey pehley kisi (nafl) namaz mein padh ley to ye namaz bhi raat ki namaz key barabar hi mutsawwir hogi."
1795,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs din aur raat mein baara rakaat (sunnat) par pabandi kerega, wo jannat mein dakhil hoga. (un ki tarteeb yun hai : ) Zohar sey pehley chaar aur baad mein do, maghrib key baad do, Isha key baad do aur Fajr (ki namaz) sey pehley do."
1796,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs baara rakaat par pabandi aur hameshgi kerega, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaeyga. (in ki tarteeb yun hai : ) Zohar sey pehley chaar aur baad mein do, Maghrib ki namaz key baad do, Isha key baad do aur Fajr ki namaz sey pehley do."
1797,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba binte Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna hai : jo shakhs din aur raat mein farz namazon key ilawa baara rakaat (sunnat) padheyga, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaeyga."
1798,"Hazrat ibne Juraij bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Ata sey kaha : mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke aap Jumey sey pehley baara rakaat padhtey hain. is silsiley mein aap ko kon si riwayat pahunchi hai? unhoney farmaya : mujhey bataya gaya hai ke Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney Hazrat Anbasaa bin Abu-Sufiyaan ko kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi din aur raat mein farz namazon key ilawa baara rakaat (sunnat) padheyga, Allah uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaeyga."
1799,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs eik din mein baara rakaat (sunnatte muakada) padheyga, Allah uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaeyga. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke Hazrat Ata ney Anbasaa sey nahin suna (jaisa ke aainda riwayat sey saaf zahir ho raha hai ke darmiyan mein Hazrat Yala bin Umayya ka wasta hai)."
1800,"Hazrat Yala bin Umayya farmatey hain ke main Taaif mein aaya to Hazrat Anbasaa bin Abu-Sufiyaan key paas gaya jabkey wo qaribul-maut they. mainey un mein ghabrahat mehsus ki to mainey kaha : (matt ghabraaiye) aap neki par qaaim hain (ya Insha Allah aap sey achchhaa sulook hoga). unhoney farmaya : mujhey meri hamsheera mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney khabar di hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs din raat mein baara rakaat (sunnatte muakada) padheyga, Allah uskey liye jannat main eik ghar bana deyga. Abu Yunus Qushairi ney in sab ki mukhalifat ki hai."
1801,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba binte Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jo aadmi eik din mein baara rakaat padhey. Zohar sey pehley (chaar, baad mein do, Maghrib key baad do, Isha key baad do aur Fajr sey pehley do) to Allah Taala uskey liye jannat main eik ghar banaeyga."
1802,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : baara rakaat aisi hain ke jo shakhs unhein (pabandi sey) padheyga, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein ghar bana deyga. chaar rakaat Zohar sey pehley aur do baad mein, Maghrib ki namaz key baad do rakaat, Isha ki namaz key baad do rakaat aur Fajr ki namaz sey pehley do rakaat."
1803,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi baara rakaat (sunnat) padheyga, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaeyga. Zohar sey pehley chaar, baad mein do, Asr sey pehley do, Maghrib key baad do aur subah ki namaz sey pehley do. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke (sanad mein mazkur raawi) Fulaih bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) Qaumi nahin."
1804,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jo shakhs din aur raat mein farz namaz key ilawa baara rakaat (sunnatey muakada) padheyga, uskey liye jannat mein ghar bana diya jaeyga : Zohar sey pehley chaar, baad mein do, Asr sey pehley do, Maghrib key baad do aur subah sey pehley do."
1805,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs din aur raat mein baara rakaat padheyga, uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaya jaeyga."
1806,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jo shakhs raat aur din mein farzon key ilawa baara rakaat padheyga, uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaya jaeyga."
1807,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jo shakhs din aur raat mein farzon key ilawa baara rakaat (sunnatey muakada) padheyga, Allah uskey liye jannat key andar ghar banaeyga. Husain ney is hadees ko marfooa bayan nahin kiya, isi ke sath us ney Anbasaa aur Musaiyab key darmiyan Zakwaan ka wasta bayan kiya hai."
1808,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jo shakhs eik din mein baara rakaat padheyga, uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaya jaeyga."
1809,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi eik din mein farz namazon key ilawa baara rakaat padheyga, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaeyga. ya (farmaya : ) uskey liye jannat mein ghar bana diya jaeyga."
1810,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eik din raat mein baara rakaat padheyga, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaeyga."
1811,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jo aadmi din mein baara rakaat padheyga, uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaya jaeyga."
1812,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs din mein farzon key ilawa baara rakaat padheyga, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein ghar banaeyga. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke ye riwayat durust nahin (yani is mein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr sahih nahin hai balke Ummul-Mominin sayeda Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ka zikr sahih hai. aur is hadees ka eik raawi) Muhammad bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) zaeef hai. wo ibne Asbahaani hai. ye riwayat is sanad (mazkura) key ilawa kaee sanadon sey bayan ki gaee hai magar in mein mazkura alfaz nahin hain."
1813,"Hazrat Hassan bin Atiya sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke jab Hazrat Anbasaa bin Abu-Sufiyaan ki wafat qarib hui to wo tadapney lagey. un sey kaha gaya (yani in ko taskeen di qaee) to unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwi mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ye bayan farmatey huye suna hai : jis shakhs ney Zohar sey pehley chaar rakaat aur Zohar key baad chaar rakaat padhin Allah Taala us ka gosht aag par haram kar deyga. jab sey mainey ye riwayat suni hai, mainey ye rakaat nahin chhodin."
1814,Hazrat Anbasaa bin Abu-Sufiyaan bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwi mohtarma aur meri hamsheera Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan kiya ke merey mehbub Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : jo bhi momin shakhs Zohar key baad chaar rakaat padhta hai to Insha-Allah kabhi bhi uskey chehrey ko aag nahin chhueygi.
1815,Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farmaya karti thi : jo shakhs Zohar sey pehley chaar rakaat aur Zohar key baad chaar rakaat (pabandi sey) padheyga to Allah Taala usey aag par haram farma deyga.
1816,"Hazrat Marwan ney kaha ke jab ye riwayat (عنبسۃ an ام حبیبۃ an النبی ﷺ) hamarey ustaad Saeed bin Abdul-Azeez par padhi jati thi to wo is ka inkar nahin kartey they balke isey barqarar rakhtey they. lekin jab wo khud ye riwayat bayan farmatey they to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr nahin farmatey they balke kehtey they ke Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Zohar sey pehley chaar rakaat aur Zohar key baad chaar rakaat padhey, Allah Taala usey aag par haram farma deyga. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Makhool ney Hazrat Anbasaa sey kuchh nahin suna. (yani ye riwayat munqata (kati hui) hai.)"
1817,Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Musa bayan kartey hain ke jab Hazrat Muhammad bin Abu-Sufiyaan ko maut aaney lagi to unhein badi ghabrahat aur be-qaraari laahiq ho gaee. unhoney farmaya : mujhey meri hamsheera mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Habiba binte Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Zohar sey pehley chaar rakaat aur Zohar key baad chaar rakaat par pabandi kerey. Allah Taala usey aag par haram farma deta hai.
1818,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Zohar sey pehley chaar aur Zohar key baad chaar rakaat (pabandi sey) padheyga, usey aag na chhueygi. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees ghalat hai. sahih hadees Marwan ki hai jo wo Saeed bin Abdul-Azeez sey bayan kartey hain."
